Welcome to my Turo profile! I'm Saman, and I'm thrilled to be part of the Turo community. With over 300 5-star reviews from satisfied customers, I take great pride in providing exceptional service and memorable experiences for all my guests.

As a passionate car enthusiast, I understand the importance of a seamless and enjoyable rental experience. Whether you're in need of a reliable vehicle for a business trip, a family vacation, or simply to explore the beauty of the open road, I've got you covered.

My fleet consists of meticulously maintained cars that are not only stylish but also safe and comfortable. I prioritize cleanliness and ensure each vehicle is spotless and in top-notch condition before every rental. Your satisfaction and peace of mind are my utmost priorities.

My commitment to excellent customer service means I'm readily available to answer any questions you may have throughout your trip. I'll provide clear communication and prompt responses to ensure an stress-free rental experience from start to finish. 

Thank you for considering renting from me. I look forward to the opportunity to serve you and provide a memorable and enjoyable car rental experience. Book with confidence and let's make your journey unforgettable!

As a car enthusiast, I understand the joy that comes with exploring new places in a stylish and reliable vehicle. My goal is to make your travel experience as smooth and delightful as possible. Whether you're here for business, pleasure, or a weekend getaway, I've got the perfect set of wheels for you.

Conveniently located in Bayside, NY and 8mins from LIRR Bayside Station, the Volvo XC60 is easily accessible, making your pick-up and drop-off hassle-free. If you need any assistance or have special requests, feel free to let me know – I'm here to help.

Your comfort and satisfaction are my top priorities. I'm more than happy to provide recommendations for local attractions, dining spots, and hidden gems to make your trip memorable. Should you encounter any issues or have questions during your rental period, I'm just a message or a call away.

I look forward to being a part of your journey and providing you with a fantastic Turo experience. Safe travels!
